{
  "texts": [
    "Coli Louvisse de Abreu et al.",
    "evaluated multiple types of toxicity of the epinephrine and norepinephrine degradation products using an ADMET predictor [151].Different from de novo drug design, there are two typical approaches to designing new drugs based on existing drug molecules.",
    "One is to screen new compounds from derivatives of FDA-approved drugs [205].",
    "In a recent study, Azamatov et al.",
    "introduced computational AMDET prediction methods to develop novel local anesthetics with lower toxicity."
  ]
}